{"tid":796451,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"你老母 個細路連人話都未識聽就咪撚學人去旅行啦","createTime":"2018-08-27T20:05:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-28T05:03:24.000Z","uid":53305,"like":70,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"8c7a9c9a1c6d80302b8fa810fb73cabc41e6c505","tid":796451,"uid":53305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-27T20:05:02.000Z","msg":"話咩留個美好回憶<br />\n屌你 個細路野都未聽得明<br />\n撚記得發生咩事<br />\n<br />\n成撚日見到啲兩三歲香港細路<br />\n係地鐵 大街跑黎跑去 無視人地當地規則<br />\n去神社參觀寫明入面要安靜 <br />\n啲父母係會由得啲細路大聲講野同大叫<br />\n係餐廳亂尻咁吠都唔理<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最仆街係坐飛機<br />\n屌你老母 今日係日本翻黎<br />\n四個鐘機 兩個細路喊足四粒鐘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n目測一個半歲仲要人手抱 一個一歲<br />\n個老豆老母仲要無理佢地<br />\n<br />\n屌你老母 我好聲好氣同個老母講<br />\n呢班係夜機 大家都要休息 你地可唔可以安撫下你兩個細路<br />\n仆街 個老母答我 有錢你搭私人飛機咪唔使嘈囉<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後佢老公加多句 細路係會喊架啦 唔係你想我點姐<br />\n<br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一直上高登連登講香港人幾閪幾自私我都唔太信<br />\n今日真係見識到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n最後 同個啲想帶細路去旅行既父母講<br />\n你個仔唔會記得你帶過佢去邊 咪撚再話咩佢會記得<br />\n除非你控制到佢 如果唔係咪撚帶去旅行<br />\n影響完人仲要唔覺得唔好意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"37980a71e20647c3aaaa21a295427c2db57539b9","tid":796451,"uid":52006,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T01:41:14.000Z","msg":"兩三歲點會唔識聽, 一係冇人教一係教都唔聽啫"},{"pid":"ebff84dd517e2b51953a426f48686a26eb4ac423","tid":796451,"uid":44277,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T01:42:56.000Z","msg":"你幾時見過日本啲兩三歲細路會咁樣亂咁喊<br />\n根本老豆老母問題"},{"pid":"6725843bdd39629eca87daedc67ab02a3f9c535b","tid":796451,"uid":97710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T01:43:14.000Z","msg":"帶小朋友去旅行唔算仆街<br />\n又唔教又唔管先係仆街<br />\n仲要搭埋凌晨機就真係仆街中既仆街"},{"pid":"844c2dbcee4919dfda2db98cf11ee75127348841","tid":796451,"uid":57513,"like":3,"dislike":7,"score":-4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T01:44:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">個個星期loop一次悶唔悶架?</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"978fdba712019303b0215267f7ffdf09c544682a","tid":796451,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6725843bdd39629eca87daedc67ab02a3f9c535b","tid":796451,"uid":97710,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T01:43:14.000Z","msg":"帶小朋友去旅行唔算仆街<br />\n又唔教又唔管先係仆街<br />\n仲要搭埋凌晨機就真係仆街中既仆街"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T01:48:12.000Z","msg":"最好唔好帶 你又辛苦 其他人又辛苦<br />\n<br />\n其實好難教<br />\n<br />\n3，4 歲細路 佢地個認知去到咩情度是個問號  可能同小貓 小狗差唔多<br />\n<br />\n佢地覺得坐飛機，坐車 <br />\n坐得耐好撚辛苦<br />\n<br />\n就<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  鳩叫<br />\n<br />\n罵，就算打都無用"},{"pid":"709439ea8db83b5dca8370e8d46a1aeafe5fd4d2","tid":796451,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-28T01:48:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>帶小朋友去旅行唔算仆街<br />\n又唔教又唔管先係仆街<br />\n仲要搭埋凌晨機就真係仆街中既仆街</blockquote>最好唔好帶 你又辛苦 其他人又辛苦<br />\n<br />\n其實好難教<br />\n<br />\n3，4 歲細路 佢地個認知去到咩程度是個問號  可能同小貓 小狗差唔多<br />\n<br />\n佢地覺得坐飛機，坐車 <br />\n坐得耐好撚辛苦<br 